{
  "title": "ISic003398. Two fragments of a building inscription",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"la\">  <span class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"aba\">fragment (physical) a</span>  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"diva--interpretive\">  <a id=\"aa-l1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span dir=\"ltr\">(vac.1)</span>PA[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"aa-l2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]mpei · CE[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] </span></div>  <span class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"abb\">fragment (physical) b</span>  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"divb--interpretive\">  <a id=\"ab-l1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>eum ❦ <br id=\"ab-l2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>Crispus · </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"la\"><span class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"aba\">fragment (physical) a</span><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"diva--diplomatic\"><a id=\"aa-l1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;PA[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"aa-l2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]MPEI·CE[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]</span></div><span class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"abb\">fragment (physical) b</span><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"divb--diplomatic\"><a id=\"ab-l1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>EUM❦<br id=\"ab-l2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>CRISPUS·</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic003398_a_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2023-05-09\" src=\"ISic003398_a_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003398_a.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2023-05-09\" src=\"ISic003398_a-thumb.jpg\"></a><a href=\"ISic003398_b_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2023-05-09\" src=\"ISic003398_b_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003398_b.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2023-05-09\" src=\"ISic003398_b-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Provisional text from photographs</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>Two fragments (0.42x0.36m and 0.415 x 0.335m), large letters 15cm high in line 1, 10cm high in line 2. The fragments do not join, but are of the same inscription probably parts of an architectural element and probably part of a building inscription. Likely restoration of the name Pompeius in the first fragment, and to be linked to the statues from the same area.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> Libertini 1926 44 b <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001874\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001874</a></li><li> Patané 2011 47 and 154 fig. 36 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001682\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001682</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1-2  100-150  Interlineation line 1 to 2  80-90  </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
